name: Tezzard Time
description: Due to the immense desire to have a tezzard I am posting the longest improv I have done yet for auction for the next 48 hours on Objkt. Once the 48 hours are past it will either be sold or burnt. Winner of the auction will get the audio from the improv along with rights to use however they want with attribution, Also, if the winner desires a different direction for the improve they can request a new improv of same or shorter length in exchange for burning the original. Contact me on Twitter DMs
